text: Shiu-Fung Jong is an I-Kiribati politician. She serves as a Member of Parliament for the Tarawa Urban constituency, from the Pillars of Truth (Boutokan Te Koaua) party. She was first elected in the 2015–16 Kiribati parliamentary election.
